show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/RfFVpk
show.description: A passionate love story between Suman, a wealthy industrialist's daughter, and Nivaan, a humble mechanic, who must endure six months of humiliation as a servant in her family's mansion to prove his worthiness. Through determination, talent, and unwavering love, Nivaan transforms from a garage worker to a successful entrepreneur, ultimately winning both Suman's hand and her family's respect.
